{{Doomwiki}}
'''Final Doom''' is the commercialization by [[Id Software]] of two [[Doom II]] {{dw|Megawad|megawads}}, ''TNT: Evilution'' and ''The Plutonia Experiment''. These two files contain all the resources from the Doom II [[IWAD]], some of them modified, as well as additional textures, making them stand-alone games rather than expansion sets.
